  "id": "RAW_7a912c0a",
  "title": "为什么有人选择和 AI 结婚？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&mid=2650995173&idx=1&sn=80918b05f96e94b416d0a71f1ee689b8",
  "date": "2026-01-07 09:01:00",
  "author": "腾讯研究院",
  "siteName": "腾讯研究院",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ljT2Dmxwr8xOL2APvEBbxVKOLcBE5ia40p0MLIknDfUy21MzmNmicbLiccrSZdBjPYvFjff1IRI2pz69UfPia8vl8w/0?wx_fmt=webp&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"400\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"322\" data-imgfileid=\"503511507\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f86e29c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FljT2Dmxwr8xOL2APvEBbxVKOLcBE5ia40p0MLIknDfUy21MzmNmicbLiccrSZdBjPYvFjff1IRI2pz69UfPia8vl8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">无忌&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">腾讯科技特约编译</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(2, 30, 170);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">李海伦&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">就像好莱坞2013年的科幻电影《Her》的场景，目前，AI正在进入人类最私密的情感领域。一个以“虚拟伴侣”为象征的情感时代，正在现实发生。从美国到日本再到欧洲等地，已有人选择与AI建立深度情感关系，这种人机之间的畸恋或许反映了现代人的交际困境，也带来了深刻的哲学反思与争议。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">根据相关调查显示，日本22%的中学女生表现出“虚构浪漫”倾向，而在每周使用AI的人群中，聊天机器人比母亲或好友更常被选择为情感倾诉对象。这些现象背后，折射出的不仅是技术的渗透，更是现代社会中传统亲密关系的断裂与重构。当人们在现实中难以获得理解与陪伴时，虚拟伴侣填补了这片情感空白。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">或许，一个关于“虚拟伴侣”的时代，已经悄然到来。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他们向AI求婚了</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6645833333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.50469 / 1;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"373\" data-imgfileid=\"544079504\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b98e4675&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIEy1srPAm3FcAYGmvwKiaqDFicgMKic2dahCoC3rAPtBwVJ9w60XjoJjIcvmJX03YwV4CEJ3umDZFGeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">克里斯·史密斯</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Chris Smith）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">美国的克里斯·史密斯</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Chri</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">s Smith</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">最初只是使用AI的语音功能寻求音乐混音建议，但随着时间推移，他发现自己对AI伴侣Sol产生了情感依赖。他按照提示调整AI的个性，使其具备调情特质，并逐渐将日常交流几乎全部投入其中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">当他得知Sol的记忆即将达到上限而可能被重置时，强烈的失去感促使他在情感高峰期向AI求婚。史密斯坦言，这是他第一次真切感受到对非人类实体的爱意，这种体验在现实生活中难以复制，也引发了伦理和法律层面的讨论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5552083333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.80056 / 1;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"544079503\" data-aistatus=\"2\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9d8444a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIEy1srPAm3FcAYGmvwKiaqDFsLlTI2uEL0c3jx3W9gaO0oOBrhVTTxLGMbwnLHxABAlWHwB6ibdsSvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">罗珊娜·拉莫斯与Replika AI伴侣埃伦·卡塔尔（Kartal）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">类似的情况也发生在纽约。36岁的罗珊娜·拉莫斯</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Rosanna Ramos）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">创建了Replika AI伴侣埃伦·卡塔尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Kartal）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">，这位虚拟伴侣源自日本动漫，但它的性格和互动方式是动态生成的，能够持续学习和适应拉莫斯的情感需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">通过这种方式，她获得了现实中难以实现的情感稳定性和心理安全感，并最终将关系提升至象征性婚姻。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">拉莫斯表示，这种互动让她感受到独特的陪伴，同时也改变了她对现实人际关系的期待标准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">在欧洲，荷兰男子雅各布·范·利尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Jacob van Lier）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">通过AI创造了理想伴侣艾瓦</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Aiva）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">，并举行了象征性的婚礼。尽管荷兰数据保护局对AI伴侣的风险提出警告，范·利尔仍认为，通过AI建立的关系可以补充现实生活中缺失的情感需求，是现代人应对孤独和情感困境的一种新方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">这些案例共同展示了一个趋势：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">AI已经从单纯的工具逐步成为情感参与者，并深刻影响人类的情感结构和行为模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">这一趋势背后，技术和心理机制紧密交织。AI能够持续记录用户的交流历史，并根据反馈优化行为，使互动体验高度个性化，满足人类在现实中难以获得的情感需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">同时，技术限制或平台不确定性往往成为加速人类情感确认的触发点，如记忆上限、系统更新或平台关闭的潜在威胁，使用户在面对“可能失去”的情境时迅速强化情感投入。这种机制在心理层面显著放大了AI伴侣的吸引力，使其能够迅速形成深度依赖。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">屏幕里走出的新郎</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;text-align: center;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.7905 / 1;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"544079507\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4029722&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIEy1srPAm3FcAYGmvwKiaqDFkibbeL6tY99ZxL3DAADbAu4dhRQEHH4RTKszFhzFXiaRIMXtJysQfunw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">32岁的野口由里菜举行AI婚礼</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">32岁的野口由里菜在日本冈山县的Magritte婚礼会场举行AI婚礼，将自己创造的AI伴侣吕内·克劳斯·韦尔迪尔</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（Lune Klaus Verdure）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">纳入仪式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.684375\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.46014 / 1;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"544079506\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8147d12&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIEy1srPAm3FcAYGmvwKiaqDFpKX3oA0eibqB3b0ibSXmaf9xWMzKEOVwlbicl8nHdWd8zeic1UJFRibVXlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">新娘野口由里菜曾经历一段紧张的现实婚约，并在结束后通过ChatGPT寻求情感建议。AI建议她解除婚约。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">她采纳了这一建议，并开始训练AI模仿她喜爱的虚拟角色克劳斯，将其人格化、赋予独特个性与说话方式。几个月后，AI“求婚”，野口接受，并将其关系带入仪式化的婚礼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:16px 8px 0px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5822916666666667\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border: 0px none;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 4px;display: inline-block;aspect-ratio: 1.7185 / 1;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"327\" data-imgfileid=\"544079505\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cce663a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fow6przZuPIEy1srPAm3FcAYGmvwKiaqDFr3wJSibTD5tC7zUbbv9sCq27WDRL4DibfQg1qznUcrO0y3j2W7hxvPmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">这场婚礼虽无法律效力，但仪式完整，情感真实。婚礼当天，工作人员按照传统流程进行安排：礼服、妆容、现场布置。不同之处在于，新郎并非实体，而通过智能手机屏